    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Accessories that project outward from the shoulder of a garment and are made of cloth or metal. In a military context, may be attached to a shoulder strap and may indicate rank or unit.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
